---
title: Creamy Chorizo & Gnocchi Soup with Baby Leaves Parmesan
description: Who said we couldn’t do soup and gnocchi because we did it and we can’t get enough of the creamy and rich flavours that are
ready to be slurped up. The chorizo gives the soup a delicious heat and the pillowy gnocchi soaks everything up.

